cast.overview: A chronicle of country music legend Johnny Cash's life, from his early days on an Arkansas cotton farm to his rise to fame with Sun Records in Memphis, where he recorded alongside Elvis Presley, Jerry Lee Lewis and Carl Perkins.
cast.title: Walk the Line

details.biography: Tyler Hilton is an American singer-songwriter and actor. Hilton began his professional career in music in 2000. Since the release of his debut album, Hilton has ventured into acting, guest starring on One Tree Hill as Chris Keller and playing the role of Elvis Presley in Walk the Line.
details.name: Tyler Hilton
